433
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:39,280
Estás bem?

434
00:45:10,480 --> 00:45:13,720
Calma, calma, ouve...

435
00:45:15,080 --> 00:45:17,440
Calma, está bem? Calma.

436
00:45:18,880 --> 00:45:19,920
Calma.

437
00:45:23,800 --> 00:45:24,800
Que...

438
00:45:28,480 --> 00:45:29,800
Ouve, eu...

439
00:45:33,160 --> 00:45:34,160
Eu...

